== BOM Project

A simple web application (rails) to play with data provided by the Australian Bureau 
of Meteorology.


== Jumpstart

1. Chekout code (assumes you already have git installed)
  >git clone git://github.com/jbrownlee/bom.git
2. Install Rails 2.3.5 (consider installing the RPM if on linux)  
  >sudo gem install rails
3. Install required gems (consider installing the RPM for JSON if on linux)  
  >sudo gem install json
4. Run:
  >cd bom
  >script/server
5. Test (in a browser): http://localhost:3000


